text: Chaohu East railway station () is a railway station of Hefei–Fuzhou High-Speed Railway in Chaohu, Hefei, Anhui. This station commenced services with Hefei- Fuzhou HSR on June 28, 2015. The station lies on the Beijing–Taipei high-speed rail corridor. ==See also== *Chaohu railway station ==References== Category:Railway stations in China opened in 2015 Category:Railway stations in Anhui
